rComments: This prof just reads off her slides and there's really no reason to go to class since she posts her slides. Also, some of her questions are really poorly worded, making her exams confusing. If you study, it's a really straight forward, easy course, but an uninteresting presentation of the information.

Teacher essentially has absolutely no idea what she is doing. Materials covered were seen probably in grade 6-7 at the most. Can barely speak English and is extremely difficult to understand. When asked to clarify, she repeats everything she just said. I am absolutely dumbfounded that this person is qualified to teach at a university level...
